WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
narrator: point the headscale CLI at the in-repo demo config.

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:10.000
narrator: users create alice — alice is now a namespace owner.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:15.000
narrator: users list shows alice alongside any earlier accounts.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:21.000
narrator: mint a preauth key alice can paste into tailscale up.

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:26.100
narrator: nodes list enumerates the machines joined to the tailnet.
